item.description:

Add this along with your other object cases:

    case PORTALID: // Home Teletab (Silabs)
        {
            teleportToX = XCOORD;
            teleportToY = YCOORD;
	heightLevel = HEIGHTLEVEL (0 = NORMAL);
        }
        break;
